To use the preferment must be taken into account to subtract the quantities of flour and water used in the preferment to the original recipe .

Example:

To add a preferment with 120grs 100grs of flour and water:

- Flour 500grs - 100grs = 400grs 
- Water 300grs - 120grs = 180grs 
- Salt 10grs
- Yeast 10grs
